column1: Is-Anti virus and-malware installed on all workstations of the bidder?
column2:
Yes, We  have an antivirus software at each critical information end point (firewalls, email servers) aand at each workstation and server. The software is configured to check all files automatically on access, downloads, and email. 
We also Install updates to antivirus software and signature files everyday.
